{"tid":386852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北泡又準備射導彈","createTime":"2017-09-04T08:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T12:47:57.000Z","uid":24345,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54066f0c4899e4a46b1ecb3e2774b94559024f8b","tid":386852,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:06:20.000Z","msg":"URGENT) S. Korea detects indications of N. Korea's ballistic missile launch preparations.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北朝鮮、弾道ミサイル発射の兆候　韓国国防省など報告<br />\n9/4(月) 15:26<br />\n朝日新聞デジタル<br />\n　韓国国防省は４日、韓国国会への報告で、北朝鮮で弾道ミサイル発射の兆候があることを明らかにした。大陸間弾道ミサイル（ＩＣＢＭ）の可能性もあるとした。米韓両国は現在、米軍の戦略爆撃機や原子力空母の朝鮮半島への派遣などについて協議しているとした。北朝鮮が３日に行った核実験の爆発規模を５０キロトン（ＴＮＴ火薬換算）と分析しているとした。（ソウル＝牧野愛博）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚煩"},{"pid":"bbb089215b5d5fd6608c711384b71161504c3f28","tid":386852,"uid":141461,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"最優秀80 後"},{"pid":"91516beeeed2bbcc76d39ba1608ffc4554947775","tid":386852,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:16:22.000Z","msg":"guam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ae038d944fb38eab03ec53182462f8f932261e","tid":386852,"uid":38671,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:20:04.000Z","msg":"金仔睇死美中得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8eb3791861975a78d2aa7d2ab6c3e88e4121902","tid":386852,"uid":7840,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:21:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c9397e28e00c05a19df414e8157de8444e1a9e7","tid":386852,"uid":5490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金仔已經睇穿美美國籠野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=