4822c6a37529","tid":386852,"uid":58358,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"其實中國成日話美國想將北韓問題外包畀中國<br />\n但事實係北韓根本係中國培養出黎既癲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家北韓失左控就話唔關中國事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100807bd3c7df5c3c7c2ca89b33e3c58984ec729","tid":386852,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:11:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實中國成日話美國想將北韓問題外包畀中國<br />\n但事實係北韓根本係中國培養出黎既癲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家北韓失左控就話唔關中國事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大6網友都話北韓係佢地養既狗。 係連登仔唔認之嘛。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d099df58dc731d57b8d29075708c870e897c7a2","tid":386852,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:11:45.000Z","msg":"肯射未"},{"pid":"b8dca3bda19addf2cea565df5e7b513a1704aac9","tid":386852,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實中國成日話美國想將北韓問題外包畀中國<br />\n但事實係北韓根本係中國培養出黎既癲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家北韓失左控就話唔關中國事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大6網友都話北韓係佢地養既狗。 係連登仔唔認之嘛。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全世界都知啦<br />\n但支那一定唔會講到明自己企北泡嗰面<br />\n所以全世界講北泡都一定燒支那之嘛<br />\n根本個個都知依兩個國家係咩關係"},{"pid":"6ee28855c714dff09ec40bc55d2982309b027cf4","tid":386852,"uid":35370,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"幫中共寫定稿先：<br />\n<br />\n中方敦促各方克制，不要對半島作出無謂的挑釁，以免引起局勢更進一步的惡化，中方高度關注事件，致力推進朝鮮半島無核化進程，希望各方尊重六方會談成果，尋求和平對話，中方再次提醒各國武力不能解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打好啦，華春瑩讀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a768cbfb1f45bfdb6454f72a434d8b5b7904f2b","tid":386852,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:20:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實中國成日話美國想將北韓問題外包畀中國<br />\n但事實係北韓根本係中國培養出黎既癲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家北韓失左控就話唔關中國事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大6網友都話北韓係佢地養既狗。 係連登仔唔認之嘛。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全世界都知啦<br />\n但支那一定唔會講到明自己企北泡嗰面<br />\n所以全世界講北泡都一定燒支那之嘛<br />\n根本個個都知依兩個國家係咩關係</blockquote><br />\n所以如果有日美國真係出師有名打北韓，都係因為中國一手造成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a1aa28a5a314597684680e06ff0851247a172b","tid":386852,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"強烈譴責<br />\n最大<del>武</del>咀力"},{"pid":"d619b1a0e504608fef5caebc501f441c76d20834","tid":386852,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外匯避險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日圓又漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要打日本都打埋，漲條毛"},{"pid":"5ebae88eaab70b7033c7cef03c30cb280cae4c55","tid":386852,"uid":9391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"9up到2046 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e55c90c12733480f8946277eff7d3b927aa26b","tid":386852,"uid":13678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:34:18.000Z","msg":"北京唔該"},{"pid":"217825b9db93f83d70b10cee11d4bcacd7f3e875","tid":386852,"uid":107885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:34:22.000Z","msg":"射得未.....二姑二姑左好耐啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" 